highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “La Jumpa” is the highest at #19.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 308 weeks straight.
“Thank God It's Christmas - 2011 Remaster” by Queen is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 100 spots at #83.
“Gato de Noche” by Ñengo Flow and Bad Bunny is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #27.
